Get ready to rumble, %PLAYERNAME%! Battles are an excellent way to bond with your Pokémon, you know.
They aren’t always about who’s the strongest, though. Battles help us test our limits and grow closer with our Pokémon, win or lose.
I want you to try out a few different kinds of battles and make note of what you learn.
Remember, the key’s to have as much fun as possible! Stick to that and you’ll always be a champ in my book!
That was great stuff, %PLAYERNAME%! Seeing you work through those tough moments was inspiring!
The road to mastering battle tactics isn’t an easy one, but you’re definitely well on your way.
Why don’t you keep challenging yourself to go further and see what else you and your Pokémon are capable of?
I’m sure we’ll run into each other again soon. In the meantime, I’ll be cheering you on!
